HEADWORD: Flashboard
<hw>Flash"board`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A board placed
temporarily upon a milldam, to raise the water in the pond above its
usual level; a flushboard.</def> <mark>[U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

